Code preview of table Film

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('FILM')
and type = 'U')
drop table FILM
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: FILM */
/*==============================================================*/
create table FILM (
FILM_ID numeric(8) not null,
KATEGORIJA_ID2 numeric(2) not null,
AUTOR_ID2 numeric(8) not null,
RESURS_ID2 numeric(8) not null,
MULTITEKA_ID2 numeric(5) not null,
TRAJANJE int not null,
MESTO_RADNJE char(50) null,
OPIS_FILMA char(256) null,
constraint PK_FILM primary key nonclustered (KATEGORIJA_ID2, MULTITEKA_ID2, AUTOR_ID2, RESURS_ID2, FILM_ID)
)
go
